<isis lang="en">
    <stitle>13 SPEED AND 18 SPEED TRANSMISSIONS EATON RTLO-713/18 SERIES - INSTALL - SHIFTER HOUSING</stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="install" graphiccount="3">
        <title>SHIFTER HOUSING</title>
        <specpara>
            <note>
                <para>There are two (2) sizes of bolts. The 1-1/2" ; bolts are used with the lifting eyes.</para>
            </note>
        </specpara>
        <para>The cooler holes on the 18-speed shifter cover cannot be used.</para>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Place the shift bars in the neutral position.</para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Place the mainshaft sliding clutches in the neutral position (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f13007r1">Figure 271</hotlnk>).
            </para>
            <figure id="f13007r1" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic id="g13007r1" filename="../figg13/G13007r1.webp" type="webp" scalefit="0"/>
                <caption>Figure 271. Place Mainshaft Sliding Clutches in Neutral Position</caption>
            </figure>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Position a new shifter housing gasket on the shifter housing mounting surface (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f13007r2">Figure 272</hotlnk>).
            </para>
            <figure id="f13007r2" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic id="g13007r2" filename="../figg13/G13007r2.webp" type="webp" scalefit="0"/>
                <caption>Figure 272. Install Shifter Housing</caption>
            </figure>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">As you install the shifter housing, make sure the yokes fit into the corresponding clutch
                gear slots and the housing aligns with the alignment bushing (18718 models) (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f13007r2">Figure 272</hotlnk>).
            </para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Apply Eaton/Fuller Sealant #71205 or Loctite 242 to the retaining bolts (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f13007r3">Figure 273</hotlnk>).
            </para>
            <figure id="f13007r3" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic id="g13007r3" filename="../figg13/G13007r3.webp" type="webp" scalefit="0"/>
                <caption>Figure 273. Tighten Retaining Bolts</caption>
            </figure>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Install the retaining bolts; tighten to 35 to 45 ft-lbs. (47 to 61 N&#183;m) (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f13007r3">Figure 273</hotlnk>).
            </para>
        </step1>
    </svcproc>
